// ================================================
// STATUS EFFECTS
// ================================================

// ================================================
// 🛡️ DEFENSIVE / PROTECTIVE
// ================================================

Substitute - (turns)
Absorbs incoming damage equal to its duration (acts like temporary HP). Removed when duration reaches 0.

Dome - (turns)
Blocks non-Genjutsu attacks. Duration decreases by 1 each time it blocks. Removed when duration reaches 0.

Earth Tank - (special)
Combines Sling + Dome + Numb on user. If Dome is already active, performs Barrage instead.

Recovered - (turns)
End-of-turn effect. If the character also has Numb, removes both Numb and Recovered.

// ================================================
// ⚡ NEGATIVE / DEBUFF
// ================================================

Doom - (turns, damage)
Start-of-turn effect. Deals set damage every turn (usually 1). Stays until duration expires or removed.

Burn - (turns, damage)
Start-of-turn effect. Deals set damage every turn (usually 1). Removed when Wet + Burn interact.

Numb - (turns)
Start-of-turn effect. Skips the character's turn and is removed immediately.

Bleed - (turns, damage)
Start-of-turn effect. Deals set damage every turn (usually 1).

// ================================================
// 💧 WATER / ENVIRONMENTAL
// ================================================

Wet - (turns)
End-of-turn effect. If the character also has Burn, removes Burn completely and reduces Wet duration by 1.

Water Clone - (turns)
Active on owner's turn: performs Barrage.  
Triggered when blocking: splashes attacker with Wet (3 turns or +2 duration).  
Also applies Wet (or +2 duration) to target after successful barrage.

// ================================================
// 🌩️ LIGHTNING / RAMP-UP
// ================================================

Charged - (turns, extraDamage)
Used by Chain Lightning. Increases number of hits on repeated use. Duration refreshes and extra hits grow with each cast.

Numb - (turns)   ← (also listed under Negative)

// ================================================
// 🔥 FIRE / HAZARD
// ================================================

Burn - (turns, damage)   ← (also listed under Negative)
Start-of-turn damage. Interacts with Wet to be removed.

Wildfire - (turns)
Active on owner's turn: deals damage + applies Burn to target and self.  
Triggered when owner is attacked: applies Burn to attacker.

// ================================================
// 🐺 BEAST / SUMMON
// ================================================

Dog - (turns)
Active on owner's turn: each Dog performs Bite (1 damage + Bleed to target, heals itself +1 duration).  
Triggered when blocking: absorbs damage equal to its duration. Removed when duration reaches 0.

Shadow Clone - (turns)
Active on owner's turn: each clone performs Barrage.  
Triggered when blocking: absorbs damage equal to its duration. Removed when duration reaches 0.

// ================================================
// 🌀 UTILITY / MISC
// ================================================

Regen - (turns, damage)
Start-of-turn effect. Heals set amount (usually 1) if below max HP.

READY - (turns)
Active on owner's turn: breaks opponent's triggered defenses then performs Barrage.

Release - (turns)
Triggered when hit by Genjutsu: removes the effect and ends turn early.
